data: {"type":"response.output_text.done","sequence_number":290,"item_id":"msg_a93834cdcf605799006933c10d171881908c19e6ef8f234eb2","output_index":1,"content_index":0,"text":"Contoso Galaxy Innovations offers a product called SmartView Glasses under the category of Smart Eyewear. Here are the detailed features:\n\n1. **Augmented Reality Interface**: This feature allows you to interact with a virtual overlay that enhances real-world surroundings. It's designed for both entertainment and practical applications.\n\n2. **Voice-controlled AI Agent**: The glasses include an AI assistant that responds to voice commands, enabling hands-free operation and assistance.\n\n3. **HD Video Recording with 3D Audio**: Capture high-definition videos enriched with three-dimensional audio, making recollections more immersive.\n\n4. **UV Protection and Blue Light Filtering**: Designed for eye health, these glasses filter harmful UV rays and blue light, reducing strain and protecting your eyes.\n\n5. **Wireless Charging with Extended Battery Life**: The product supports convenient wireless charging and features an extended battery life to ensure longevity throughout the day.\n\n**Additional Information**:\n\n- **Warranty**: Offers a two-year limited warranty on all electronic components.\n- **Return Policy**: A flexible 30-day return policy with no questions asked.\n- **User Guides**: Includes sections such as finding the right fit, proper care, troubleshooting, and safety tips to maximize product experience.\n\nFor further assistance or inquiries, customers can reach out to Contoso's support via email at support@contoso-galaxy-innovations.com.","logprobs":[]}

